{
  "texts": [
    "• Medium evolution model 2+1D viscous hydro (\"VISHNU\") that has been calibrated against light particle production observables.",
    "• Feed down implementation Feed down contributions from 2 S, 3 S, 1P, and 2P states for ϒ states.",
    "• Comparisons to experimental data Can describe ϒ(nS) data from both LHC and RHIC collisions, except for the recent ϒ(3 S) data from CMS since recombination of ϒ(3 S) has not been included.",
    "• Phenomenological breadth We included ϒ(nS) and χ b (n P) in the reaction network.",
    "We studied both RHIC and LHC collision energies."
  ]
}